OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny morning fog patches quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a fine and sunny day
OL,7,Ffor all. Winds light, so feeling very
OL,8,Fwarm or hot in the strong July
OL,9,Fsunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPlenty of sunshine through
OL,12,Fthe evening, then staying clear
OL,13,Fovernight. Some mist and fog patches
OL,14,Fforming during the early hours.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FMorning mist and fog patches
OL,17,Fquickly clearing to leave a fine and
OL,18,Fvery warm, locally hot day, with
OL,19,Fplenty of sunshine. Light winds
OL,20,Fthroughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
